17:54.006 --> 17:55.497
'Cause that's an excuse.

17:55.608 --> 17:57.041
I've been on my own
since I was six.

17:57.143 --> 17:58.975
Look at me. I didn't quit.
I ain't a loser.

17:59.078 --> 18:00.170
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.

18:00.279 --> 18:01.576
You ain't never been
in the jug, either.

18:01.681 --> 18:03.945
That's 'cause I was never
stupid enough to steal.

18:04.951 --> 18:06.509
Now, you got a choice.

18:06.619 --> 18:08.382
You can go out there,
make a fresh start.

18:08.487 --> 18:10.717
Or you can stay in here
and be a bathroom attendant.

18:10.823 --> 18:12.723
It's not me, it's them.

18:12.825 --> 18:14.156
