what he's talking about.

19:03.976 --> 19:06.036
You gonna be a singer,
you gonna be a loser?

19:11.484 --> 19:12.508
Singer.

19:12.618 --> 19:13.517
I knew that!

19:13.619 --> 19:15.610
I... I knew that.

19:17.890 --> 19:19.722
