19:28.234 --> 19:30.634
Whoa!

19:37.309 --> 19:40.404
CROWD: Go home, jailbirds!
Go home, jailbirds!

19:40.513 --> 19:42.743
Pizzazz...

19:46.085 --> 19:48.076
Go home, jailbirds!

19:48.187 --> 19:50.918
